                     <interp inst="t18000917-56-person604" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , the constable, produced the lace, which was deposed to by Mrs. Williams.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's defence. I am innocent of the charge.</p>
               <p>
